From 0000000000000000000000000000000000000000 Mon Sep 17 00:00:00 2001
From: Ondrej Jirman <megi@xff.cz>
Date: Wed, 11 Feb 2026 21:20:13 +0100
Subject: arm64: dts: allwinner: Increase clock-latency-ns to 2ms

Real time needed for OPP change must include voltage regulator update
delay and other delays.
---
